"doc_user_agreement" = "Welcome to AI Assistant. Please read this user agreement before using the app.\n\n1. Service Description\nThe app provides AI chat, multilingual translation, and scenario learning. Features may change over time; please refer to in‑app descriptions.\n\n2. Account & Security\nYou may use some features as a guest, or register/log in for full features and data sync. Keep your account information safe; you are responsible for any loss caused by your actions.\n\n3. User Conduct\nYou must follow laws and public order. Do not use the service for illegal or harmful activities. We may restrict or terminate service for violations.\n\n4. Privacy & Data\nWe respect your privacy. See the Privacy Policy and in‑app Settings for details. We will not share your personal information with third parties without consent.\n\n5. Agreement Changes\nWe may update this agreement and notify you in the app. Continued use means acceptance of changes.";
