"doc_terms_of_service" = "These Terms of Service, together with the User Agreement, form the agreement between you and AI Assistant.\n\n1. Service Content\nAI Assistant provides AI‑based chat, translation, and learning support. Availability may be affected by network, device, or maintenance; we aim for stability but cannot guarantee it.\n\n2. Disclaimer\n1) AI‑generated content is for reference only and is not professional advice. For important decisions, consult professionals.\n2) We will assist within legal limits for issues caused by force majeure, network failures, or third‑party service problems, but we do not assume liability beyond what the law requires.\n\n3. Intellectual Property\nThe app’s UI, text, and marks are owned by us or rights holders. No copying, modification, or commercial use without authorization.\n\n4. Dispute Resolution\nDisputes are governed by the laws of the People’s Republic of China. If unresolved, the court with jurisdiction where the operator is located shall apply.";
